#

Creamy Herb Potato Bake

60 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

AmericanComfort Food

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodBakedCheesy

Description

A comforting and creamy baked dish that elevates simple potatoes with fresh herbs and savory cheese.

Ingredients

  • potatoes: 4 large
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • grated cheese (cheddar or mozzarella): 1 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh herbs (like rosemary or thyme): 2 tablespoons
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
